'''CenturyTel of Missouri, LLC''' is a telephone operating company owned by [[CenturyLink]] that provides local telephone service in [[Missouri]]. The cities served by the company include [[Branson, Missouri|Branson]] and [[Columbia, Missouri|Columbia]].
The company was established in 2002 upon CenturyTel's purchase of lines from [[Verizon Communications]]. The lines in Missouri were transferred from [[GTE Midwest]], which was originally an operating company of [[GTE]]. That company was dissolved following the 2002 sale.
